external_knowledge:
Highly engaged users are those who frequently interact with a website, resulting in a higher total engagement score; 
Conversion refers to the user completing a desired action, such as making a purchase or filling out a form; 
Average session duration refers to the average length of time a user spends on the website per session; 
A long session history indicates a user's loyalty to the website.
